summary: An ordinance relating to the vacation of West Armour Street from the east line of the alley between 33rd Avenue West and 34th Avenue West to the west line of the alley between 32nd Avenue West 33rd Avenue West and certain other avenues and alleys, authorizing the Superintendent of Parks to sign a petition therefor, being City Comptroller's File No. 216307 and repealing Ordinance No. 80914.
